Params: {1: '1', 3: 'Rosetta, who should have been ahead to clear the way, is instead waiting for you and the others on the snowfield.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Rosetta', 3: "We're almost there, so I've been waiting here for you.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Rosetta points her spear off into the distance through the misty snowfield, following her spear tip, you see familiar port facilities at the edge of the snowy forest.'}
{1: '1', 3: "Kyaranta's liaison greets you warmly. However, upon hearing the intention of your visit, he gives you a snide look."}
{2: 'Liaison', 3: "Go further north from here. They're located at the abandoned dock over there.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liaison', 3: "But... If you expect to just sail 'em out right away, I'm afraid that won't be so easy.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liaison', 3: 'But let me tell you, Kyaranta has no objections to this. Take them if you want.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liaison', 3: "I'm sure you must all be tired from your voyage. Why don't you rest here for the night?", 4: '1'}
